Class UserSOAP

  • java.lang.Object
    • wsd.ass.soap.UserSOAP

  • public class UserSOAP
extends Object
    The UserSOAP class defines the functions to be used by the SOAP web service in relation to users. It communicates with the UserApplication class to retrieve data from user.xml
